:

*Traže* ljubav, ali je ne nalaze. (They are looking for love, but they don't find it.)
*Pretraživali* su sve moguće opcije. (They were searching through all possible options.)
*Posmatrali* su nebo za znakove. (They were looking at the sky for signs.)
*Nisu* mogli da pronađu odgovor. (They couldn't find the answer.)
*Tražili* su pomoć od svog prijatelja. (They were looking for help from their friend.)